questions.quote: Hi! Oh yeah, uh-huh, it's me. I saw you grab your running shoes this morning and sneak out. You lied so you could run by yourself.
Oh...wait...you two think of me as family?! Oh, I have to ask you something now and be honest; do you want me to sing Careless Whisper or Lady In Red?
No, no, no, don't! I've been waitin' for like, forever to go out with Lorraine. Just calm down.
Oh, I-I gave them the puppy and it made them so happy that I decided I'm gonna carry their baby.
Okay, so I'm responsible, I'm organised. But hey, I can be a kook.
But I'm unemployed, my music is all I really have now. Well music, and making my own shoes. Pretty, huh?
No, no-no, she was a human lady. This is the spirit of my Mom Lily, the one who killed herself.
Oh y'know, I didn't think of it that way. You're right. You're right. So, can I ask you a question?
I'm okay. I gotta go down to the police station and look at mug shots.
Oh umm, y'know I think it would be better if we just save it.
